Package: MotIV
Type: Package
Title: Motif Identification and Validation
Version: 1.2.1
Date: 2010-02-09
Author: Eloi Mercier, Raphael Gottardo
Maintainer: Eloi Mercier <eloi.mercier@ircm.qc.ca>, Raphael Gottardo <raphael.gottardo@ircm.qc.ca>
Imports: graphics, grid, IRanges, lattice, methods, rGADEM, stats, utils
Suggests: rtracklayer
Description: This package makes use of STAMP for comparing a set of motifs to a given database (e.g. JASPAR). It can also be used to visualize motifs, motif distributions, modules and filter motifs.
License: GPL 2
biocViews:  Microarray, ChIPchip, ChIPSeq, GenomicSequence

